==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Overhang
<hw>O`ver*hang"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <vmorph>[<pos>imp. &
p. p.</pos> <conjf>Overhung</conjf> <pr>(?)</pr>; <pos>p. pr. & vb.
n.</pos> <conjf>Overhanging</conjf>.]</vmorph> <sn>1.</sn> <def>To
impend or hang over.</def> <mark>[R.]</mark> <rj><au>Beau. &
Fl.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>To hang over; to jut or project over.</def>
<rj><au>Pope.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Overhang</ent>⟦br⟧

